<p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: Farside Investors, US spot Bitcoin ETF flow data (2024); Glassnode, illiquid supply and short-term holder SOPR on-chain metrics (2024); Balchunas, E., Bloomberg Intelligence ETF analysis commentary (2024); Chainalysis, on-chain seller-attribution methodology; public Bitcoin daily close and liquidation data (January-December 2024).</p>
